docs.text: Welcome to WallTokens This website is a support for the paper WallToken . You can find the design files and the code in the "Files" section. Pictures of the tokens can be found in the "Pictures" section. More information about the project and th authors in "About" section. For full documentation visit mkdocs.org . Commands mkdocs new [dir-name] - Create a new project. mkdocs serve - Start the live-reloading docs server. mkdocs build - Build the documentation site. mkdocs -h - Print help message and exit. Project layout mkdocs.yml # The configuration file. docs/ index.md # The documentation homepage. ... # Other markdown pages, images and other files.
